! This is a geometry definition file in the dbin format.
!
! The structure of each detector component is defined by a 
! template definition in its included db/*.db file. 
! For documentation of the structure of a component,
! consult its template definition file.
!
! This file expects the subsystem template files to reside in
! directory db/ under the directory from which dbin or a program
! that uses dbin is run. The easiest way to provide this directory
! is to make a link to the db directory under the top level of the
! mcfast distribution, eg.
!    ln -s ~bphyslib/mcfast/test/db db
!
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------
